bothered making a way station is simply due to the fact that it would
cost too much for fuel way out there.

Likewise, you\'re very screwed if you do misjump in there.  You\'ve got
absolutely nothing to point yourself too.  Theoretically, if someone
really goofed up they could just low berth themselves and point their
