Tamer\'s Handbook_ is off by a factor of 11-13 (as compared to the prices in
the TNE rulebook) and the ACR that is the sole example of weapons in _Fire,
Fusion & Steel_ is more that 5 times more expensive than the ACR in the
main rules.
    So I thought I\'d like to reality check those weapons that I have a chance
of checking: those that are commonly available on Earth today. Unfortunately
