Wrongo. we 1995 earthers can hit outter planets at 10+AU with really stupid
little probes using ion thrusters (post launch). Now add on-board guidance.
Forget lasers, they spread too much.

>> And they don\'t have to vaporize it, just crack it into smaller masses and its
>> course will change or the peices will be vaporized by atmospheric
