	But Jump Torpedoes ARE cannon. They can be found in the CT
adventure "Leviathan" published by GDW. They do not damage the background
of Classic Traveller; they are an indispensible part of it. The
challenge is to come up with an explanation consistent with canon why
jump torpedoes are POSSIBLE. There are no design rules for them as far
as I know. Rules need to be made that mesh well with existing starship
design rules so that players can fully explore the potential of
these devices. The problem is that design rules from Book 2, Book 5,
Striker and MT are not consistent with one another.

