    'body' => 'Hi There:

> Can anyone explain to me how sandcasters are supposed to work in CT
> The rules say that a DM of -3 is applied to hit for every 25mm of 
> obscuring sand.  So I take it one launches sand from one\'s sandcaster,
> but then I get confused.  If the sand laucher rolls a "hit" (8+) does
