     <Do you have a list of  known ancient sites, especially in the Domain of
Deneb?>   The following is part 2 of a file by Clay Bush on the ancients:

                             Regina Subsector

Yori
(University of Regina)

   This small site is characterized by iridescent white building
blocks and occasional deep rubble-filled wells.  It was found
buried in a vast desert, surrounded by signs of destruction from
the Final War.

Beck\'s World
(University of Regina)

   Somewhat larger than the Yori site, it is a collapsed warren of
interlocking caverns.  It is only partially excavated.

Efate
       (IISS)

   Operated as a historic site.  Restorations show a gridwork of
thousands of walls spaced about two meters apart, and punctuated by
extremely massive bulwarks at random intervals.
   Discovered in 354, it has long since been stripped of any useful
items.

Pixie (Secret)
       (IISS)

